Short doctrine version

You could store it like this:

Spider routes and translates.
Hypatia verifies.
Mirror refines and aligns.
Frogman narrativizes.
Hound tracks outcomes.
Badger governs attention and boundaries.
Mother Duck archives primitives.
Goblin Financier allocates execution.
Indigo Hammer stress-tests.
Chronos-Mesh stabilizes time.
Nomicon keeps roles and names coherent.

That gives you a pretty complete operating cast.

The one thing I’d tighten next is a formal daemon-to-engine registry spec so nothing drifts or overlaps.